NOTE

For development environment specific settings to apply,
	make sure your url starts with 'localhost.'.

	ex:
		http://localhost.garagesale.com/


INSTRUCTIONS

1. Duplicate '/protected/config/local.php.sample' to '/protected/config/local.php'
	then edit it to match your local environment configuration.

2. Rename '/db_rebuild.php.danger' to '/db_rebuild.php'.
	Enter 'http://localhost.garagesale.com/db_rebuild.php' in your browser for a clean database,
	OR 'http://localhost.garagesale.com/db_rebuild.php?populate' for a populated one.

3. FOR MAC USERS:
	Run '$ bash mac' in your local repository.